-- Fifteen Dead in India Train Fire; 25 Injured, Official Says
-- B y   B i b h u d a t t a   P r a d h a n
-- 2012-07-30T04:02:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-30/fifteen-dead-in-india-train-fire-25-injured-official-says.html
The death toll in a passenger train
fire in southern  India  rose to at least 15, with 25 injured,
Indian Railway Spokesman Anil Saxena said.  One coach of the Tamil Nadu Express caught fire while
passing through the state of Andhra Pradesh, he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
